This repo forks Wheel of Fortune Bingo by Jeremy Rue to build a solution for running a Wheel of Fortune style spinner powered by Streamer.Bot for your streams.

My primary usecase for this can been to do a virtual spinner for the BeanBoozled Spicy Bean challenge

There's currently still some work to do on refining the code and writing up docs so it's pretty raw right now. When there's time/interest I'll look to polish this up further